Reasoning: The paper deals with the Degrees of Freedom (DoF) of a MIMO Interference Channel (IC), which is a topic in Information Theory (cs.IT). The use of MIMO technology and the study of channel matrices suggest that it could also belong to the sub-categories of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) and Signal Processing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the optimization of MIMO operations, which could fall under Multimedia (cs.MM) and Computer Engineering (cs.CE).
